" to be canceled*"
msgstr ":guilabel:`全额退款`：贷记单自动验证并与发票对账。*如果已验证的发票需要取消，可选择此选项*。"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales.rst:59
msgid ""
