#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/track_and_bill.rst:111
msgid ""
"Once the :abbr:`SO (sales order)` has been confirmed, click the "
":guilabel:`Create Invoice` button. This will open a :guilabel:`Create "
