msgstr ""
"确认:abbr:`SO（销售订单）` 后，单击 :guilabel:`创建发票` 按钮。将打开一个 :guilabel:`创建发票` 弹窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/track_and_bill.rst:114
